high_descs: Turn around and stand in front of the stove.
Pick up the pan from the stove.
Go right and stand in front of the fridge.
Open the fridge door and set the pan on the top shelf, shut the door, open the door and then take out the pan and shut the door.
Turn around and go to the stove and stand in front of it.
Put the pan on the back, left burner.
anns.task_desc: Put a cooled pan on the stove.

high_descs: Turn right, then turn right again, then go forward and turn right to face the stove.
Take the pan from the stove.
Turn around, go straight, then turn left to go to the fridge.
Chill the pan in the fridge.
Turn around, then turn right to approach the stove.
Put the pan on the stove, on the back left corner.
anns.task_desc: Put a chilled pan on the stove.

high_descs: Turn around and walk towards the stove on your right.
Pick up the black pan on the left side of the stove.
Cool the pan in the fridge and take it back out.
Turn around and head towards the stove on your right.
Place the pan back to the original spot.
anns.task_desc: Cool down the pan on the stove.
